]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T12:09:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131289523,imgsize-830756.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[France bans Israel minister Ben-Gvir over mocking detained Gaza flotilla activists]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131289305.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/france-bans-israel-minister-ben-gvir-over-mocking-detained-gaza-flotilla-activists/articleshow/131289305.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/france-bans-israel-minister-ben-gvir-over-mocking-detained-gaza-flotilla-activists/articleshow/131289305.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T11:56:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI News Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131289426,imgsize-72806.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[From Hormuz to nuclear talks - what to expect in the 60-day US-Iran ceasefire proposal]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288866.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A potential 60-day ceasefire extension between the US and Iran is nearing, aiming to reopen the Strait of Hormuz and allow Iranian oil exports. This deal, brokered by Pakistan, includes lifting US port blockades and sanctions waivers, contingent on Iran negotiating its nuclear program and ending the Israel-Hezbollah conflict. Global oil markets are closely monitoring developments.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-hormuz-to-nuclear-talks-what-to-expect-in-the-60-day-us-iran-ceasefire-proposal/articleshow/131288866.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/from-hormuz-to-nuclear-talks-what-to-expect-in-the-60-day-us-iran-ceasefire-proposal/articleshow/131288866.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T10:32:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288889,imgsize-804993.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Obsession with our country's most cherished structure': Trump reacts to White House shooting]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288789.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US President Donald Trump praised the Secret Service and law enforcement for their swift action in neutralizing a gunman near the White House. The suspect, identified as Nasire Best, was killed after firing at agents. Trump highlighted the incident's importance for future presidential security, referencing a previous security breach.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/obsession-with-our-countrys-most-cherished-structure-trump-reacts-to-white-house-shooting/articleshow/131288789.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/obsession-with-our-countrys-most-cherished-structure-trump-reacts-to-white-house-shooting/articleshow/131288789.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T10:21:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288812,imgsize-966519.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Either we sign a deal or hit them harder': Trump says Iran deal has '50/50' chances]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288330.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump indicated a 50/50 chance of a deal or military action with Iran, with a decision expected Sunday. Intense diplomatic efforts involving multiple Middle Eastern nations have led to a "largely negotiated" Memorandum of Understanding for peace, subject to finalization.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/either-we-sign-a-deal-or-hit-them-harder-trump-says-iran-deal-has-50/50-chances/articleshow/131288330.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/either-we-sign-a-deal-or-hit-them-harder-trump-says-iran-deal-has-50/50-chances/articleshow/131288330.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T09:23:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288382,imgsize-34980.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[School, residential buildings hit as Russia pounds Ukraine capital Kyiv with missiles, drones; 1 dead]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288343.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/school-residential-buildings-hit-as-russia-pounds-ukraine-capital-kyiv-with-missiles-drones-1-dead/articleshow/131288343.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/school-residential-buildings-hit-as-russia-pounds-ukraine-capital-kyiv-with-missiles-drones-1-dead/articleshow/131288343.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T09:26:17+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288461,imgsize-235664.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Iran refutes Trump's 'largely negotiated' deal, claims to keep Hormuz control]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288119.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Donald Trump announced a significant deal with Iran is nearing completion. This agreement aims to reopen the Strait of Hormuz and end ongoing hostilities. While Iran has pushed back on some claims, discussions are ongoing. Regional leaders have expressed support for the peace efforts. The proposed deal also addresses Iran's nuclear program.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-refutes-trumps-largely-negotiated-deal-claims-to-keep-hormuz-control/articleshow/131288119.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-refutes-trumps-largely-negotiated-deal-claims-to-keep-hormuz-control/articleshow/131288119.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T08:48:25+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288214,imgsize-807413.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[White House shooting: 21-year-old Nasire Best, who identified himself as Jesus Christ, shot dead]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131287947.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A 21-year-old man, Nasire Best, who allegedly believed he was Jesus Christ, was killed by Secret Service after opening fire outside the White House. Best had a history of loitering and violating orders to stay away from the complex. The incident triggered a lockdown and injured at least one bystander.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/white-house-shooting-21-year-old-nasire-best-who-identified-himself-as-jesus-christ-shot-dead/articleshow/131287947.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/white-house-shooting-21-year-old-nasire-best-who-identified-himself-as-jesus-christ-shot-dead/articleshow/131287947.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T07:50:33+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131287985,imgsize-1044060.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Taiwan detects Chinese military aircraft, naval vessels near island for second straight day]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131288010.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Taiwan's defense ministry reported Chinese military activity, with four aircraft and six naval vessels detected around the island. Three aircraft crossed the Taiwan Strait median line. This follows a day of heightened activity, with 16 aircraft and eight vessels observed, 13 of which crossed the median line. These incursions underscore rising regional tensions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-detects-chinese-military-aircraft-naval-vessels-near-island-for-second-straight-day/articleshow/131288010.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-detects-chinese-military-aircraft-naval-vessels-near-island-for-second-straight-day/articleshow/131288010.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T08:01:26+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131288024,imgsize-582946.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Iran agrees to give up enriched uranium as deal with Trump 'largely negotiated': Report]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131287875.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran has reportedly agreed in principle to surrender its enriched uranium stockpile to the US as part of a peace deal. This significant concession, aimed at de-escalating tensions and reopening the Strait of Hormuz, comes after US military threats. While a deal is "largely negotiated," final details on the uranium transfer and broader nuclear talks are pending.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-agrees-to-give-up-enriched-uranium-as-deal-with-donald-trump-largely-negotiated-report/articleshow/131287875.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-agrees-to-give-up-enriched-uranium-as-deal-with-donald-trump-largely-negotiated-report/articleshow/131287875.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T07:23:36+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131287901,imgsize-806521.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Mayday! SA scientists identified hantavirus outbreak in 24 hours]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131287556.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mayday-sa-scientists-identified-hantavirus-outbreak-in-24-hours/articleshow/131287556.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mayday-sa-scientists-identified-hantavirus-outbreak-in-24-hours/articleshow/131287556.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-24T05:34:24+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131287585,imgsize-76834.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[White House gunfire scare: Footage shows journalists running for shelter]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131287497.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDAT